{"type":"message","id":"159bd0e9","parentId":"a382f786","timestamp":"2026-04-17T03:33:31.640Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-17 03:33:31 UTC] Summarize latest AI news from last 24 hours.\nSystem: \nSystem: Focus on:\nSystem: - LLMs\nSystem: - RL\nSystem: - Diffusion models\nSystem: - VLM / robotics\nSystem: \nSystem: Output:\nSystem: - 5 bullet points\nSystem: - Why it matters (2 lines)\n\nA scheduled reminder has been triggered. The reminder content is:\n\nSummarize latest AI news from last 24 hours.\n\nFocus on:\n- LLMs\n- RL\n- Diffusion models\n- VLM / robotics\n\nOutput:\n- 5 bullet points\n- Why it matters (2 lines)\n\nHandle this reminder internally. Do not relay it to the user unless explicitly requested.\nCurrent time: Friday, April 17th, 2026 — 3:33 AM (UTC) / 2026-04-17 03:33 UTC"}],"timestamp":1776396811631}}
{"type":"message","id":"57f3aa53","parentId":"159bd0e9","timestamp":"2026-04-17T03:33:51.350Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"ollama_call_7ba76462-eb55-466a-b168-25bf5761e016","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"latest AI news LLMs RL diffusion models VLM robotics last 24 hours","count":5,"date_after":"2026-04-16"}}],"stopReason":"toolUse","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"qwen-local:latest","usage":{"input":8057,"output":58,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":8115,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1776396831348}}
{"type":"message","id":"2a8219be","parentId":"57f3aa53","timestamp":"2026-04-17T03:33:51.391Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"ollama_call_7ba76462-eb55-466a-b168-25bf5761e016","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"error\": \"missing_brave_api_key\",\n  \"message\": \"web_search (brave) needs a Brave Search API key. Run `openclaw configure --section web` to store it, or set BRAVE_API_KEY in the Gateway environment.\",\n  \"docs\": \"https://docs.openclaw.ai/tools/web\"\n}"}],"details":{"error":"missing_brave_api_key","message":"web_search (brave) needs a Brave Search API key. Run `openclaw configure --section web` to store it, or set BRAVE_API_KEY in the Gateway environment.","docs":"https://docs.openclaw.ai/tools/web"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776396831389}}
{"type":"message","id":"e2615f95","parentId":"2a8219be","timestamp":"2026-04-17T03:34:10.363Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"It seems there was an issue with fetching the latest AI news from Web using Brave Search API. This appears to be due to a missing API key.\n\nTo resolve this, you'll need to configure the Brave Search API key in your OpenClaw setup:\n\n1. **Run `openclaw configure --section web`** to store the API key.\n2. Alternatively, set the `BRAVE_API_KEY` environment variable for an automated configuration.\n\nOnce configured correctly, I can fetch and summarize the latest AI news from last 24 hours focusing on LLMs (Large Language Models), RL (Reinforcement Learning), diffusion models, VLM (Vision-Language Models), and robotics. Then, I'll provide a concise summary with explanations of their importance.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"ollama_call_ef7b2c40-4f6b-4100-96e3-52c7b65d8ddf","name":"web_search","arguments":{"date_after":"2026-04-16","query":"latest AI news LLMs RL diffusion models VLM robotics last 24 hours","count":5}}],"stopReason":"toolUse","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"qwen-local:latest","usage":{"input":8198,"output":207,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":8405,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1776396850359}}
